        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Immuno-EM detects the protein in dendrites, spines, and also axons.\n\nFig. S1G supports the EM findings by biochemical fractionation of mouse brain: the protein is mostly found (by Western blot) in the post-synaptic and pre-synaptic fractions.. Experimental description: male C57BL/6J at P21" ;
